  <diagram name="Page-1" id="LSROcZTHMT349L5mbVzo">
    <mxGraphModel dx="2597" dy="1133" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="850" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <mxCell id="iUqdiNfp9wn8bgnYZjvP-3" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="instagram&amp;nbsp; hld&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="60" x="70" y="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="iUqdiNfp9wn8bgnYZjvP-4" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="FUNCTIONAL REQ-&lt;div&gt;1.user should be able to see the post of the person they are following .&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2.user shuld be able to post the content on social media(image text and videos)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3.user should be able to like and comment the post in social media.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4.user should be able to creatre an account in instagram .&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;5.the feed should be generated according to the user engagement .&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;6.user can be followed and can follow other user on insta.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;7.&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="120" width="690" x="-10" y="120" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="iUqdiNfp9wn8bgnYZjvP-5" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;NON-FUUNCTIONAL REQ-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;1.instagram should be available most of the time.....aailablity&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;consistency&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;2.it should handle the request for atleast 1 million in a day&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;3.the latency should be not more than 200ms for liking and commenting .&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;4.the latency for the content upload should be not more than 1000ms .&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;5. the content should filter non-policy content&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;6.the system shoulfd&amp;nbsp; be reliable no data loss of post&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;7. the feed loading latency should be less than 400ms for smooth scrolling&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="210" width="700" x="-50" y="280" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
